New Episode of The East Wing with Adam Stacoviak

By Tim Smith · November 8th, 2012

I recorded a new episode of The East Wing this week with Adam Stacoviak. For those of you who don't know him, he's a really nice guy. He host three podcasts himself and on the show we talk about podcasting and his role as Product Lead at Pure Charity.
